data.description: Lovely home on large corner fenced lot! This well-maintained home has an open floor plan and excellent flow, new appliances, and a fresh coat of exterior paint. Large master suite with walk-in closet. Indoor laundry, extra deep garage, and a big back deck, perfect for summer entertaining. Spacious yard features RV parking and tool shed. Call your agent today for a showing!
